## Config for the pdf reader zathura

## Key mappings (for Colemak)
map e scroll down
map u scroll up
map n scroll left
map i scroll right

map E scroll half-down
map U scroll half-up

map <PageUp> navigate previous
map <PageDown> navigate next

map q quit
map Z quit

set scroll-step 70

set font inconsolata

# ## COLORS
set default-bg #002b36
set inputbar-bg #002b36
set inputbar-fg #839496
set statusbar-bg #073642
set statusbar-fg #93a1a1
set notification-error-bg #dc322f
set notification-error-fg #002b36
set notification-warning-bg #b58900
set notification-warning-fg #002b36
set completion-bg #073642
set completion-fg #93a1a1
set completion-highlight-bg #859900
set completion-highlight-fg #002b36

# customize pdf colors with CTRL-i
set recolor-lightcolor #002b36
set recolor-darkcolor #839496
